OL,6, leather sofas coming off the production
OL,7, line at Man Wah Furniture's factory in 
OL,8, Monterrey are 100% "Made in Mexico".   
OL,10,FThey're destined for large retailers in
OL,11,Fthe US, like Costco and Walmart. But   
OL,12,Fthe company is from China, its Mexican 
OL,13,Fmanufacturing plant built with Chinese 
OL,14,Fcapital.                               
